data.description: Come and be amazed at this, stunningly, gorgeous home located in the prestigious Dove Creek gated community. Prepare to be captivated by the sheer beauty and elegance that abounds in every corner of this two-story masterpiece. Step inside and experience the sensation of grandeur as you are greeted by an open-concept floor plan that effortlessly flows from one room to the next. The seamless integration of the living and office space, creates an atmosphere of warmth and togetherness, perfect for both entertaining and productivity. The kitchen is accented by timeless stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, ample cabinetry, and a smooth cook-top for all the cooking enthusiasts. Enjoy dinners in your eat-in kitchen either from bar stools pulled up to the island bar, or from the dining area table nestled conveniently to the side of the kitchen. Up the custom stairs, a sprawling loft/game room awaits, ready to be transformed into a realm of endless possibilities. Wind down from a long day in the peaceful refines of your spacious and inviting Owner's retreat, equipped with all the charming amenities to provide comfort and relaxation.  The secondary bedrooms are equally as spacious and inviting. From the custom flooring that exudes sophistication and elegance, to the absence of carpet that adds a touch of modernity and convenience, every aspect has been meticulously crafted to perfection. The covered patio invites you to unwind and bask in the beauty of the surrounding natural landscape and wildlife, providing a sanctuary for quiet contemplation or lively gatherings with loved ones. The propety is equipped with a 6-zone irrigation systems which allows for ease of watering and upkeep. Enjoy the luxury of having your home back a natural greenbelt, affording you the privacy that abounds within this unmatched, premier community. Situated right next to the neighborhood pool and neighborhood park, endless hours of fun and recreation are just steps away. Embrace a lifestyle of leisure and excitement as you take advantage of the amenities that await you in this vibrant community. Conveniently located close to Lackland Air Force Base, Hwy 1604 & 90, HEB, and an abundance of dining and shopping options, this home ensures that you will never have to venture far. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional home your very own.
